{
  "stem": "2718.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I know that there were quite a number of people who-- who didn't arrive to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not that it would have made any difference.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it made a difference to the-- to the family, knowing that their father or their mother were-- was lying next to them in the wagon dead.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Of course, it might had been.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But by that time, people-- people lost feeling for-- you know, everybody was so [INAUDIBLE] inclined.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everybody was just think of his own, very own life, very own survival, and their-- and their children's survival.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was-- it was a terrible situation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Parents who were respected by the children, grandparents, they-- they were helpless.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "All-- all deprived of any sort of authority, which a parent can exercise over a child.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was simply on animal level.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Absolutely animal level.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "People who-- who were very private and very-- very introverted, they-- they had to go-- they had to-- they go to the toilet among 75 other people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean-- I mean, I don't think there's any need to describe the-- the-- the feeling of people, of-- or how they must have felt-- how-- how a person, a grandmother must have felt when-- when-- when the daughter or the grandchild had to help her with-- with her everyday business, which she wouldn't have dreamt of even talking about, never mind doing it in public.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Or-- so I think the last bit of-- of dignity was just-- was just stripped away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The train stopped-- the train stopped the first time-- from the time it started, it stopped in a place called in Hungarian, Kasha, and in Czech, Kosice.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was practically the border between-- between Poland-- not far from the border anyway.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
